    <text>

        <front>
            <div type="editorial_desc">
                <p>Uncle Sam and a Spanish matador are at a bar having a drink.  They both wink and hold weapons behind their backs.  Uncle Sam holds are revolver and the matador holds a knife.</p>
            </div>
        </front>

